- Get off.

08:00.416 --> 08:02.791
I'll swab the deck for a week.

08:04.125 --> 08:05.165
What?

08:05.166 --> 08:06.874
If you let me
do the night watch.

08:06.875 --> 08:08.750
I'll swab the deck for a week.

08:13.208 --> 08:14.291
Month.

08:15.250 --> 08:16.208
Deal.

08:17.375 --> 08:19.208
