- Uh-huh!

08:23.416 --> 08:24.708
What are you after?

08:25.750 --> 08:26.750
Nothing.

08:27.875 --> 08:28.958
Okay...

08:29.791 --> 08:30.750
You're on.

08:36.291 --> 08:38.041
- Now, you know what to do?
- Yeah, yeah.

08:39.916 --> 08:42.374
- Do not mess up.
- I won't.

08:42.375 --> 08:43.625
You'd better not.

08:51.625 --> 08:54.000
