- Yeah, yeah. Just go to bed.

09:23.250 --> 09:25.749
Ah!

09:25.750 --> 09:27.832
Good girl.

09:27.833 --> 09:29.582
Good girl, Stella.

09:29.583 --> 09:31.583
Good girl.

09:32.625 --> 09:34.041
Good girl, Stella.

09:36.625 --> 09:37.957
No, no, no!

09:37.958 --> 09:39.624
Stella, Stella!

09:39.625 --> 09:41.124
Come here. Come back here.

09:41.125 --> 09:42.374
Stella... Argh!

09:42.375 --> 09:44.374
Stella, come here.

09:45.583 --> 09:48.249
