09:57.291 --> 09:58.749
- Michael.
- What's going on?

09:58.750 --> 09:59.999
- Michael!
- Becky,

10:00.000 --> 10:01.582
- why aren't you at the wheel?
-Michael!

10:01.583 --> 10:02.749
