in a home.

11:20.666 --> 11:22.124
Becky!

11:54.041 --> 11:55.832
Come here,
you silly old thing.

11:55.833 --> 11:56.874
Come here.

11:56.875 --> 11:58.499
Good girl.

11:58.500 --> 12:00.749
Get off.

12:07.625 --> 12:08.957
Okay, she can stay.

12:08.958 --> 12:10.374
Yay!

12:10.375 --> 12:12.582
