12:20.833 --> 12:22.124
And swab the deck,
you hear me?

12:22.125 --> 12:23.374
Aye aye, Skipper.

12:23.375 --> 12:25.332
Eh, he's not the Skipper.

12:31.833 --> 12:33.332
Gross.

13:51.458 --> 13:53.416
Michael,
clear all that stuff away.

13:54.333 --> 13:56.665
Argh. It's bad out there.

13:56.666 --> 13:58.915
