I think she'll hold.

13:58.916 --> 14:01.541
Well, let's hope so. Now,
come and have a look at this.

14:02.458 --> 14:04.499
The nearest land
is a day away.

14:04.500 --> 14:05.999
You think we can outrun it?

14:06.000 --> 14:07.999
