gonna have to weather it.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.874
Isn't there even
a tiny island somewhere?

14:09.875 --> 14:11.665
We're in
the middle of nowhere.

14:11.666 --> 14:13.540
If we'd only held back a bit.

14:13.541 --> 14:15.040
But if we can
get to here,

14:15.041 --> 14:16.207
maybe a bit more shelter?

14:16.208 --> 14:17.874
And wait for it
to blow past.

14:17.875 --> 14:20.040
We need to get Stella
from her kennel.

14:20.041 --> 14:22.540
But what if we head this way?
Or this?

14:22.541 --> 14:24.540
No,
this is our only option.

14:24.541 --> 14:26.249
Someone needs to get Stella!

14:26.250 --> 14:27.915
God knows
the size of these swells.

14:27.916 --> 14:28.999
