14:34.625 --> 14:36.457
I can't see
in this bloody light.

14:36.458 --> 14:38.124
Let's just focus
on one thing at a time.

14:38.125 --> 14:39.540
Wait. No, no, no, no, no, no.

14:39.541 --> 14:41.290
No! No, you don't.

14:41.291 --> 14:43.540
