- Let go!

14:51.166 --> 14:52.707
Dad!

14:53.791 --> 14:55.875
Michael, no!

15:12.333 --> 15:13.291
Stella.

15:16.000 --> 15:16.958
Come on.

15:19.250 --> 15:21.250
Whoa. Come on.

15:23.125 --> 15:24.500
Michael!

15:26.000 --> 15:27.666
Hurry, Michael. Quick!

15:28.916 --> 15:30.291
No!

15:33.166 --> 15:34.957
Michael!

15:46.291 --> 15:49.375
No. Michael!

16:10.875 --> 16:12.749
Help!

16:12.750 --> 16:14.791
Help!

16:15.666 --> 16:16.833
Help...

16:26.791 --> 16:28.208
Stella, Stella!

16:28.958 --> 16:30.665
Stella, help!

16:59.666 --> 17:01.207
